summary-text:
It’s the first NEO dev competition
-- an event that is all about creation, passion and ambition.
This global get-together of NEO community developers
will put you amongst streams of inspiration and
collisions of intelligence.
Join us and be inspired.
rules1: The competition was open on Nov. 20, 2017 and will be closed at 23:59 Mar. 31, 2018. Please sign up and submit your work before the deadline.
rules2: Participants are required to develop on NEO blockchain. Please refer to github.com/neo-project and docs.neo.org for relevant codes and technical docs.
rules3: During the competition that spans one and a half months, developers are free to team up and deliver their work in collaboration.
rules4: Submission time slot will be Nov. 20, 2017-Mar. 31, 2018. Those who fail to submit their work before the deadline will be marked ineligible.
rules5: Your submission must contain executable programs and codes.
issue gas: Note: GAS will be issued at the same value.
